\[
\overline{uv}=UV+\overline{u'v'},
\]

\end_inset

若 
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{u'v'}\ne0$
\end_inset

，则称 
\begin_inset Formula $u$
\end_inset

 与 
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

 是
