\end_inset

，即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
|u'|\ll|U|,
\]

\end_inset

则
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\ev{\frac{\partial u}{\partial t}}_{T}\equiv\frac{1}{T}\int_{t}^{t+T}\frac{\partial u}{\partial t}\dd{\tau}\approx\frac{U(\vec{r},t+T)-U(\vec{r},t)}{T}\approx\frac{\partial U}{\partial t},
\]

\end_inset

即时间导数与时间平均这两种运算依然可交换。
\end_layout

